title: Catalonian independence will be won at the ballot box — Josep Ganyet — Perspective with Alison Smith
description:
This week, on Perspective with Alison Smith: Spain in crisis over Catalonia's fight for independence

We hear from Josep Ganyet who supports Catalonia’s pursuit for secession from Spain

Watch the full episode at cpac.ca/perspective
